text: Dimboola is a 1973 film. It is a filmed recording of a performance of Jack Hibberd's play of the same name by the Australian Performing Group at The Pram Factory. ==Cast== *Bruce Spence *Fay Mokotow *Wilfred Last *Rosslyn de Winter *Tim Robertson *Jan Friedl *Charles Kemp *Robert Meldrum *Evelyn Krape *Peter Cummins *Jude Kuring *Eileen Chapman *Bill Garner *Kerry Dwyer *Jack Charles *Max Gillies ==Production== The film was shot during an actual performance at the Pram Factory, Carlton, Melbourne on the evening of 22 May 1973. ==External links== *Dimboola at Oz Movies * Category:1973 films Category:Australian comedy-drama films Category:Australian films Category:Australian films based on plays
title: Dimboola (1973 film)
